Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪中散去的再不斬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡幹嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了這麼多人又是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 再不斬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你死在這兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果請正規忍者 可是要花很多錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會僱傭你們這些叛忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能順便讓你們這些忍者互相殘殺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以節約我很多金錢和時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼霧隱鬼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼裡不過是個滑稽的小丑罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙從哪兒冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我不用去殺達茲納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跟你打下去也沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子跟我還有點有過節呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然害本大爺骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 這小子已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是開口說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的遺體被那樣糟蹋 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點感覺都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了他一直伴隨在你左右嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就像是卡多在利用我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是在利用白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們忍者只不過是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的 是他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…毫無依戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們與他的戰鬥已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從心底喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很重要的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那麼地喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當一個人一心想保護重要的東西時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的可以變強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點感覺都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為真正的忍者是很難的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的完全不在乎他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想實現他的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我願意成為真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想變得像你一樣厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻只得到這種結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己的命都不要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要實現他的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己的夢想也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像工具一樣死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是太殘酷了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白不只是為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了你們才決意要戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比誰都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是個老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠跟你們交手真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許無法成為沒有感情的工具…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 把你的苦無借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們快去幹掉那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為靠自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打贏這麼多人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼…鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然那麼想見同伴的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己一個人去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒打算…跟白去同一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…你還想逞強…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和本大爺一起…下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧隱鬼人下了地獄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以變成真正的鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟是不是小丑到地獄就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了…白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走來 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別轉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個努力活下去的男人最後的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不可以動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 鳴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個戴面具的傢伙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個戴面具的少年已經死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鳴人殺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了掩護再不斬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是佐助 躲過了致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙打從一開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助沒事了 他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白也是為了你們才決意要戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是個老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下放心了 佐助也平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們開心得太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易找到的僱主就這麼被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我們乾脆襲擊城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把值錢的東西都拿走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一下子就能解決這些人的忍術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我消耗了太多的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們敢再靠近這座島一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要動用所有的武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們有來無回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄總是遲一些登場的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也來助你們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我現在的查克拉也能虛張聲勢一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西版
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…再看看那傢伙的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種季節竟然會下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭泣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 你都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…最後時刻讓我能在你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…想和你去同一個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出生在一個白雪皚皚的村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像雪一樣潔白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 再不斬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者存在意義真的像他們說的一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以追尋自身存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像工具那樣存在才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點連我們木葉也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂真正的忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以忍者都不知覺地活在這個困擾中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像再不斬和那個孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走我自己的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一條絕對不會後悔的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托各位的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大橋已經建成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會非常寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達茲納大叔 我還會再來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會覺得很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭就哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥才是 想哭就哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就愛逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年改變了伊那利的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利改變了村民的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年為我們搭建了邁向希望的勇氣之橋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到橋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒給大橋取名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想到一個超級適合這座橋的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「鳴人大橋」如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓伊魯卡老師請我吃拉麵慶祝任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓木葉丸知道我的英勇事跡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 回村之後跟我約會好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我約會吧 我隨時奉陪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 鳴人 你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要取這個名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望這座大橋永遠都不會垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:21:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且有一天會成為舉世聞名的大橋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要叫這個名字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第七班最近老是執行一些簡單的任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明打敗了\N像再不斬和白那樣厲害的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼更能讓我施展身手的任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的忍道和心都燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的篇章 晉級中忍的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的忍道
